sentences: Roger Sanchez (born June 1, 1967) is a Dominican-American house music DJ, remixer and producer.
He won a Grammy Award for his remix of "Hella Good" by No Doubt in 2003, and is best known for his song "Another Chance", which was an international hit in 2001.
